										font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;'><b>Glossįrio: </b>Registra a decisćo que transfere a execuēćo da pena a outro juķzo territorialmente distinto.</td></tr><tr style='background-color: white'><td> </td><td width='20' nowrap>
								  <font style='color:red;'>Cancelamento da distribuiēćo</font> 
							  </td><td> </td><td> </td><td> </td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >83</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >3</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >CPC 2015</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >290</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' >2008-09-30 15:52:47</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><tr><td align=left valign=top colspan='9' 
										style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;
										font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;'><b>Glossįrio: </b><p>
	Registra a decis&atilde;o que determina o cancelamento da distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o, em qualquer hip&oacute;tese, inclusive no caso de n&atilde;o recolhimento de custas dentro do prazo de trinta dias.</p>
<p>
	<span style="font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35px;"><font face="Arial" style="font-size: 10pt;">Art. 290. Ser&aacute; cancelada a distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o do feito se a parte, intimada na pessoa de seu advogado, n&atilde;o realizar o pagamento das custas e despesas de ingresso em 15 (quinze) dias.</font></span></p>
</td></tr><tr style='background-color: white'><td> </td><td width='20' nowrap>
