	<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Art. 922.</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;Convindo as partes, o juiz declarar&aacute; suspensa a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o durante o prazo concedido pelo exequente para que o executado cumpra voluntariamente a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>
