									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td></tr><tr style='background-color: white'><td> </td><td> </td><td width='20' nowrap>
								  <font style='color:#800000;'>Absolviēćo sumįria - crimes dolosos contra a vida</font> 
							  </td><td> </td><td> </td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >11877</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >385</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >CPP</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >415</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' >2011-10-19 00:00:00</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><tr><td align=left valign=top colspan='9' 
										style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;
										font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;'><b>Glossįrio: </b><p>
	Movimento a ser utilizado quando for realizada a absolvi&ccedil;&atilde;o sum&aacute;ria do r&eacute;u, no momento previsto no art. 415 do CPP.</p>
<p>
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">Art. 415.&nbsp; O juiz, fundamentadamente, absolver&aacute; desde logo o acusado, quando: <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font> <font face="Arial" size="2"> </font></p>
<p align="justify" class="texto2">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I &ndash; provada a inexist&ecirc;ncia do fato; <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify" class="texto2">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; II &ndash; provado n&atilde;o ser ele autor ou part&iacute;cipe do fato; <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify" class="texto2">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; III &ndash; o fato n&atilde;o constituir infra&ccedil;&atilde;o penal; <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify" class="texto2">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IV &ndash; demonstrada causa de isen&ccedil;&atilde;o de pena ou de exclus&atilde;o do crime. <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify" class="texto2">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.&nbsp; N&atilde;o se aplica o disposto no inciso IV do </span><span style="color: black;"> caput</span><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;"> deste artigo ao caso de inimputabilidade prevista no </span> <span style="color: black;">caput</span><i><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;"> </span></i><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">do art. 26 do Decreto-Lei n<u><sup>o</sup></u> 2.848, de 7 de dezembro de 1940 &ndash; C&oacute;digo Penal, salvo quando esta for a &uacute;nica tese defensiva. <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11689.htm#art1">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 11.689, de 2008)</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify">
	Movimento criado na reuni&atilde;o do Comit&ecirc; Gestor do dia 21/03/2011.</p>
</td></tr><tr style='background-color: white'><td> </td><td> </td><td width='20' nowrap>
								  <font style='color:#800000;'>Absolviēćo Sumįria do art. 397-CPP</font> 
							  </td><td> </td><td> </td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >11876</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >385</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >CPP</td><td  align=left nowrap
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;' >397</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' >2011-10-19 00:00:00</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' >2011-10-19 17:16:23</td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><td  align=right
									style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;width:150px;' ></td><tr><td align=left valign=top colspan='9' 
										style='font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;
										font-size: 8pt;font-weight:300;'><b>Glossįrio: </b><p>
	Movimento a ser utilizado quando for realizada a absolvi&ccedil;&atilde;o sum&aacute;ria do r&eacute;u, no momento previsto no art. 397 do CPP.</p>
<p>
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">Art. 397.&nbsp; Ap&oacute;s o cumprimento do disposto no art. 396-A, e par&aacute;grafos, deste C&oacute;digo, o juiz dever&aacute; absolver sumariamente o acusado quando verificar:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11719.htm#art1">(Reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Lei n&ordm; 11.719, de 2008).</a></span></font> <font face="Arial" size="2"> </font></p>
<p align="justify">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I - a exist&ecirc;ncia manifesta de causa excludente da ilicitude do fato;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11719.htm#art1">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 11.719, de 2008).</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; II - a exist&ecirc;ncia manifesta de causa excludente da culpabilidade do agente, salvo inimputabilidade;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11719.htm#art1">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 11.719, de 2008).</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; III - que o fato narrado evidentemente n&atilde;o constitui crime; ou&nbsp;<a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11719.htm#art1">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 11.719, de 2008).</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify">
	<font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IV - extinta a punibilidade do agente. <a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2007-2010/2008/Lei/L11719.htm#art1">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 11.719, de 2008).</a></span></font></p>
<p align="justify">
	Movimento criado na reuni&atilde;o do Comit&ecirc; Gestor do dia 21/03/2011.</p>
</td></tr><tr style='background-color: white'><td> </td><td> </td><td width='20' nowrap>
